{"tid":280044,"cid":23,"subCid":0,"title":"相機多重曝光功能初體驗","createTime":"2017-06-11T18:48:25.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-13T00:43:39.000Z","uid":74640,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"90a2c74756c9d775e26f5d656be3661bd9e20cd4","tid":280044,"uid":74640,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T18:48:25.000Z","msg":"部80D入手未夠一季<br />\n無意中發現有多重曝光功能<br />\n玩落又好似幾正<br />\n唔知大家平時點用e個功能呢<br />\n小弟想學下野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/12/024823_278eaf800016b43d03f5d42b22f63fbb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F12%2F024823_278eaf800016b43d03f5d42b22f63fbb.jpg&h=ef695b3c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"dfb76f4bbe649c7a02b69c1b120034562b4989f7","tid":280044,"uid":57643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T18:49:31.000Z","msg":"咩叫多重曝光<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n求教"},{"pid":"bd81e7e75af447f66ecabdfdec0e399e238daa1f","tid":280044,"uid":27485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T18:53:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咩叫多重曝光<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n求教</blockquote><br />\n合二為一"},{"pid":"8a8c037e427e0bc46094917df4c1fe1f60936b01","tid":280044,"uid":40867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T18:54:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咩叫多重曝光<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n求教</blockquote><br />\n回想翻菲林時代<br />\n你知道菲林點運作的話 就好容易解釋<br />\n只係同一張菲林影兩次<br />\n兩個不同影像係同一張菲林曝光 兩個影像就會重疊 就好似樓主個張 一張係天空 一張係地面<br />\n<br />\nbtw計過角度 係咪黃大仙個邊"},{"pid":"268b675a1827281bf0c5602584cdac4fe68834c1","tid":280044,"uid":74640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T18:57:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>咩叫多重曝光<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n求教</blockquote><br />\n回想翻菲林時代<br />\n你知道菲林點運作的話 就好容易解釋<br />\n只係同一張菲林影兩次<br />\n兩個不同影像係同一張菲林曝光 兩個影像就會重疊 就好似樓主個張 一張係天空 一張係地面<br />\n<br />\nbtw計過角度 係咪黃大仙個邊</blockquote><br />\n相中有地點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9be525766977de199efcd9774e8f1371dee5e8a","tid":280044,"uid":75627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T19:00:32.000Z","msg":"富山嚟"},{"pid":"7cd78063a1d7202811481102a5cf71fa5d3fac1c","tid":280044,"uid":10842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T19:05:24.000Z","msg":"個月亮點影到咁大？"},{"pid":"467c440f42b0b35cdcef35cb591a0d95bf63d4b4","tid":280044,"uid":19068,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T19:06:23.000Z","msg":"是咪google下都懶...<br />\n<br />\n重曝簡單一句姐係疊相，可以透過後製整番出嚟。<br />\n而家啲相機都有呢個功能，先影一張，後影一張。樓上巴打講解左，係以前菲林機時代嘅一種攝影方法，你唔過張菲林，都可以繼續係個格菲林上開快門曝光。<br />\n<br />\n我自已用重曝多數會咁玩<br />\n<br />\n影張效果<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/12/025804_fb2ba9fdba12bc2fcb4b3f2c8f43f186.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F12%2F025804_fb2ba9fdba12bc2fcb4b3f2c8f43f186.jpg&h=a59430e1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n影張主體<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/12/025806_c61f23fcd50955d86b401a9cca6c4240.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F12%2F025806_c61f23fcd50955d86b401a9cca6c4240.jpg&h=25cac517&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n出嚟效果<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/12/025808_5fbe55d3157c15e4ef792da455b47d22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F12%2F025808_5fbe55d3157c15e4ef792da455b47d22.jpg&h=15fa5b18&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n即刻用app整多張例子<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/12/030538_c001729d5e35eac89a3e0438751442d8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F12%2F030538_c001729d5e35eac89a3e0438751442d8.jpg&h=5ddd3c40&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"454d990b8d438f8959e2cb1805e07c6519d32d64","tid":280044,"uid":19068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T19:08:50.000Z","msg":"時代進步，而家啲單反有好多功能同設定，可以研究多少少，唔好嘥左部靚機。"},{"pid":"edd75c6e2bcc454236734d2c6535e788632b4164","tid":280044,"uid":9142,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T19:12:45.000Z","msg":"樓主呢張係咪影左個天&amp;月亮+屋邨景？<br />\n睇唔出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8a6edde32240f0ab6b9098fd2c127615fcc6abf","tid":280044,"uid":19068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T19:17:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓主呢張係咪影左個天&amp;月亮+屋邨景？<br />\n睇唔出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n可能個月咁大係zoom左埋去影再合落張屋邨相到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea62e7362c3ba3da9963a1e737ca93da69eedfd5","tid":280044,"uid":89928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T19:29:32.000Z","msg":"想問點影到個月亮咁清<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我快門較得慢啲個月亮就散開晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"487d8680727c56f0515d2116b4cb3aed7a0057e9","tid":280044,"uid":57568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T19:35:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>想問點影到個月亮咁清<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我快門較得慢啲個月亮就散開晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n同問<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1f8f362907f60bf252acf164fd82f326d03ce84","tid":280044,"uid":14934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T20:58:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>想問點影到個月亮咁清<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我快門較得慢啲個月亮就散開晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n同問<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n細光圈，快快門，主點測光？"},{"pid":"32b1164a342b11adeb7955fcf46c3c65e9b44439","tid":280044,"uid":70227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T22:23:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>想問點影到個月亮咁清<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我快門較得慢啲個月亮就散開晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n同問<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n細光圈，快快門，主點測光？</blockquote><br />\n後製"},{"pid":"8f0262b56f1e64ef3d18757b92b9ba2773ab4d1b","tid":280044,"uid":17190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T00:55:43.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://photoblog.hk/121222/%E4%B8%8D%E7%94%A8-nd-%E6%B8%9B%E5%85%89%E9%8F%A1%EF%BC%8C%E4%B9%9F%E5%8F%AF%E5%9C%A8%E7%99%BD%E5%A4%A9%E6%8B%8D%E6%94%9D%E9%95%B7%E6%9B%9D%E7%85%A7%E7%89%87%E7%9A%84%E7%A7%98%E8%A8%A3/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fphotoblog.hk%2F121222%2F%25E4%25B8%258D%25E7%2594%25A8-nd-%25E6%25B8%259B%25E5%2585%2589%25E9%258F%25A1%25EF%25BC%258C%25E4%25B9%259F%25E5%258F%25AF%25E5%259C%25A8%25E7%2599%25BD%25E5%25A4%25A9%25E6%258B%258D%25E6%2594%259D%25E9%2595%25B7%25E6%259B%259D%25E7%2585%25A7%25E7%2589%2587%25E7%259A%2584%25E7%25A7%2598%25E8%25A8%25A3%2F&d=N8xYUS4A8HlYY7RRcLmgcJ7TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=f0867584\" target=\"_blank\">https://photoblog.hk/121222/%E4%B8%8D%E7%94%A8-nd-%E6%B8%9B%E5%85%89%E9%8F%A1%EF%BC%8C%E4%B9%9F%E5%8F%AF%E5%9C%A8%E7%99%BD%E5%A4%A9%E6%8B%8D%E6%94%9D%E9%95%B7%E6%9B%9D%E7%85%A7%E7%89%87%E7%9A%84%E7%A7%98%E8%A8%A3/</a><br />\n<br />\n多重曝光也可以這樣用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6cc58600315e4e01420a31a5c2f1d7a52dccdac","tid":280044,"uid":74640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T01:36:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>想問點影到個月亮咁清<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我快門較得慢啲個月亮就散開晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n同問<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n正常單影月亮ISO 100-200 / 快門 1/160-200 光圈最大<br />\n但因為相機個多重曝光功能係第一張相同第二張相個ISO 一樣<br />\n而我係手持無腳架<br />\n所以影月亮我係iSo 2000 / 光圈5.6/ 1/2000"},{"pid":"df703147f897377df460c8ed3f94979956060809","tid":280044,"uid":79471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T01:38:31.000Z","msg":"和邪?"},{"pid":"7c72e712f6687af289f460df74ab2293abe9f73f","tid":280044,"uid":54655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T01:41:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>想問點影到個月亮咁清<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我快門較得慢啲個月亮就散開晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你點影啫？"},{"pid":"9979d83ce5a256ae1b5151beefb55f35a21f4500","tid":280044,"uid":74640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T02:49:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>想問點影到個月亮咁清<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我快門較得慢啲個月亮就散開晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你點影啫？</blockquote><br />\n快門慢會變左白色一大點"},{"pid":"02d87c5efb6ad4840755446f14cecf7c7495a97d","tid":280044,"uid":54655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T03:27:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>想問點影到個月亮咁清<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我快門較得慢啲個月亮就散開晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你點影啫？</blockquote><br />\n快門慢會變左白色一大點</blockquote><br />\n咁係over啫，唔係散開哂"},{"pid":"11262ae9ed423e7820ef87ee2b7787cc6284d00e","tid":280044,"uid":74640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T03:44:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>是咪google下都懶...<br />\n<br />\n重曝簡單一句姐係疊相，可以透過後製整番出嚟。<br />\n而家啲相機都有呢個功能，先影一張，後影一張。樓上巴打講解左，係以前菲林機時代嘅一種攝影方法，你唔過張菲林，都可以繼續係個格菲林上開快門曝光。<br />\n<br />\n我自已用重曝多數會咁玩<br />\n<br />\n影張效果<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/12/025804_fb2ba9fdba12bc2fcb4b3f2c8f43f186.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F12%2F025804_fb2ba9fdba12bc2fcb4b3f2c8f43f186.jpg&h=a59430e1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n影張主體<br />\n[im]<a href=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/12/025806_c61f23fcd50955d86b401a9cca6c4240.jpg[/img]\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F12%2F025806_c61f23fcd50955d86b401a9cca6c4240.jpg%5B%2Fimg%5D&d=N8xYUS4A8HlYY7RRcLmgcJ7TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=a539e74e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/12/025806_c61f23fcd50955d86b401a9cca6c4240.jpg[/img]</a><br />\n<br />\n出嚟效果<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/12/025808_5fbe55d3157c15e4ef792da455b47d22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F12%2F025808_5fbe55d3157c15e4ef792da455b47d22.jpg&h=15fa5b18&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n即刻用app整多張例子<br />\n[ig]<a href=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/12/030538_c001729d5e35eac89a3e0438751442d8.jpg[/img]\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F12%2F030538_c001729d5e35eac89a3e0438751442d8.jpg%5B%2Fimg%5D&d=N8xYUS4A8HlYY7RRcLmgcJ7TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=8cd6440e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/12/030538_c001729d5e35eac89a3e0438751442d8.jpg[/img]</a></blockquote><br />\n你相張相我有睇過有興趣咁影"},{"pid":"b3a8cdd5b8c85d91dbfd70f05f57310b0416d79b","tid":280044,"uid":71341,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T09:40:00.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"bf36e4e93f0a8eb4a41572b05e464e2b505f82f9","tid":280044,"uid":71341,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T09:42:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"469a7a73df345cba5f79ececff255d9539841104","tid":280044,"uid":9128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T13:57:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"http://i1376.photobucket.com/albums/ah10/blankcathk/DSC01145_zps4xmwtp89.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi1376.photobucket.com%2Falbums%2Fah10%2Fblankcathk%2FDSC01145_zps4xmwtp89.jpg&h=a120b67d&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n影埋哂啲無里頭荷花定唔知係蓮花<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好撚on9"}]}